mimalloc
------------------------------------------
mimalloc (pronounced 'me-malloc') is a general purpose allocator with
excellent performance characteristics. Initially developed by Daan Leijen for
the run-time systems of the Koka and Lean languages.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.5-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libmimalloc-devel-3.1.5-1bl1
  libmimalloc3-3.1.5-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cmake-4.1.3-1
  cygport-0.37.6-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/microsoft/mimalloc

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/microsoft/mimalloc/archive/refs/tags/v3.1.5.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack mimalloc-3.1.5-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./mimalloc-3.1.5-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mimalloc-3.1.5-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/mimalloc-3.1.5-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmimalloc3-3.1.5-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmimalloc-devel-3.1.5-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(mimalloc)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/mimalloc.README
  /usr/share/doc/mimalloc/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/mimalloc/readme.md

(libmimalloc3)
  /usr/bin/cygmimalloc-3.dll

(libmimalloc-devel)
  /usr/include/mimalloc-new-delete.h
  /usr/include/mimalloc-override.h
  /usr/include/mimalloc-stats.h
  /usr/include/mimalloc.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/mimalloc/mimalloc-config-version.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/mimalloc/mimalloc-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/mimalloc/mimalloc-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/mimalloc/mimalloc.cmake
  /usr/lib/libmimalloc.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/mimalloc.pc

